edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.annotations

Annotation Type MOperator


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface MOperator
    Annotation interface for operators. Bound to the field holding the operator as a lambda expression over atoms.

      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
